<!-- FAQ -->
<div class="section fade-up">
  <div class="section-title">Frequently Asked <span>Questions</span></div>
  <p class="section-sub">Everything you want to know before ordering.</p>
  <div class="faq-list">
    <div class="faq-item open">
      <div class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
        Is this a genuine business or a fraud? <span class="faq-arrow">+</span>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-a">We are a real business based in Secunderabad, Hyderabad. We have delivered 500+ orders across the city. You can verify us on our Instagram page where you will find real customer delivery videos. Our godown is in Secunderabad and we deliver through verified delivery partners across all Hyderabad areas.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <div class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
        Why is there a Rs.99 advance payment? <span class="faq-arrow">+</span>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-a">The Rs.99 is only to confirm your order slot and book your delivery. It is not a payment for the product. It is 100% refundable — if you reject the product during open box delivery, we refund the Rs.99 immediately. If you accept, it is adjusted in your final payment.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <div class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
        What is open box delivery? <span class="faq-arrow">+</span>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-a">Open box delivery means our delivery person waits while you open and check the product completely. Test the earbuds, check the sound, check the charging — everything. Only if you are 100% satisfied, you pay the remaining amount in cash. If anything is wrong, send it back right then and there. Zero risk to you.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <div class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
        How fast is delivery in Hyderabad? <span class="faq-arrow">+</span>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-a">Orders placed before 2 PM are delivered the same day. Orders placed after 2 PM are delivered the next morning. We cover all areas of Hyderabad including Secunderabad, Ameerpet, LB Nagar, Dilsukhnagar, Madhapur, Kondapur, Begumpet, Uppal, and everywhere in between.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <div class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
        What if the product stops working after delivery? <span class="faq-arrow">+</span>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-a">We provide a 3-month seller warranty on all products. If anything stops working within 3 months of purchase, WhatsApp us with a video of the issue and we will either replace the product or resolve the issue. Our customer support is real and responsive.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <div class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
        Are these original Apple AirPods? <span class="faq-arrow">+</span>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-a">No, these are premium TWS earbuds inspired by the AirPods Pro design. They are not original Apple products. The sound quality, bass, and build are excellent for the price point. We are completely transparent about this — you are getting premium quality audio at a fraction of the Apple price.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <div class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
        Can I order if I am outside Hyderabad? <span class="faq-arrow">+</span>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-a">Currently we only deliver within Hyderabad for same-day open box delivery. We are working on expanding to other Telangana cities soon. If you are outside Hyderabad, please WhatsApp us and we will see what we can arrange.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

